# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — __hash__, __eq__, __lt__ across all 6 decimal subjects
#
# 6 classes x 3 methods = 18 rows.
# decimal.Decimal: __hash__ = true (Decimal objects are hashable),
# __eq__ = true (Decimal objects support == numeric comparison),
# __lt__ = true (Decimal objects support < numeric ordering).
# This true/true/true pattern is the key finding of wave 675 for the decimal
# module: Decimal fully implements hash, equality, and ordering protocols.
# All other decimal classes (Context, DecimalException, InvalidOperation,
# Overflow, Underflow): false for all three operators.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

